author: HarleyG
title: Great starter set
review: I got this set for $20 AUD and it has been a lot of fun for my 3yo son. To start with it has 3 duplo people that can relate as mummy, daddy & son. The car is big enough to fit at least 2 people inside (all 3 if the child stands) and there are a variety of different pieces that relate to the real world.
